<h2 class="bold font-l">Apple Slices & Storytime</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When Eda and King has trouble dealing with the baby bats, Eda says there's only one solution and whips out a knife... which she uses to cut some apple slices while preparing to read them a story. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
